      },
      {
        "text": "幽州境",
        "label": "LOC"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_034_000058",
    "sentence": "出兵不過九月，還師不過十二月。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "九月",
        "label": "TME"
      },
      {
        "text": "十二月",
        "label": "TME"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_034_000059",
    "sentence": "在路不得見僧尼、喪服之人。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_034_000060",
    "sentence": "皇帝親征，留親王一人在幽州，權知軍國大事。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "皇帝",
        "label": "TITLE"
